Importing and Cleaning Data
```{R}
data4b <- read.csv("~/dsan-5000-project-kendallgilbert180/dsan-website/5000-website/data/00-raw-data/4b.csv", header=FALSE, comment.char="#")
data4b <- setNames(data4b, c("Country","2000","2001","2003","2004","2005","2006","2007","2008","2009", "2010", "2011","2012","2013","2014","2015","2016","2017", "2018", "2019", "2020", "2021"))
data4b[data4b == ".."] <- NA
```

Exporting Data 
```{R}
write.csv(data4b, file = "cleandata4b.csv", row.names = TRUE)

```
